Package io.github.noeppi_noeppi.libx.datapack

Class DynamicElementDatapack

java.lang.Object
io.github.noeppi_noeppi.libx.datapack.DynamicElementDatapack
All Implemented Interfaces:
AutoCloseable, net.minecraft.server.packs.PackResources, net.minecraftforge.common.extensions.IForgePackResources
public class DynamicElementDatapack extends Object implements net.minecraft.server.packs.PackResources
A datapack that provides some dynamically json files at fixed locations. The jsons are generated by encoding an element using a Codec. To add your elements, call addEntry(ResourceLocation, Codec, Supplier) in the constructor. The elements are lazily initialised, that means the supplier is called only once, when the element is first queried.
